author: gbrown
msg: Eliminate padding style from TerraFrameSkin and TerraSheetSkin (in most cases, a padding style will be supported by the window's content, so this style is somewhat redundant in TerraFrameSkin; in TerraSheetSkin, setting padding to a non-zero value actually produces the wrong UE, as the content appears to slide out from the padding rather than the top of the window).
